# The American Dream - placeholder art, one file per technology.
# To replace any of these with real art just overwrite
#   gfx/interface/technologies/tad/<technology name>.dds
# keeping the same filename. Nothing else needs editing.
# Both GFX_<tech>_medium and GFX_USA_<tech>_medium are defined because a
# country-specific sprite overrides the generic one.

